The paper focuses on the impact of software evolution on software metrics, which is a key concern in software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also proposes an automatic approach to examine the hypothesis, which involves analyzing software code (cs.PL). The paper presents experiments conducted on multiple software systems, which involves software development (cs.SD). The paper also involves data analysis and statistical modeling, which falls under machine learning (cs.MS) and data analysis (cs.LG).
